-- Istithmar Says It Is `Supportive' of Loehmann's, Working to Save Company
-- B y   C o l i n   K e a t i n g e
-- 2010-10-29T13:40:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-29/istithmar-says-it-is-supportive-of-loehmann-s-working-to-save-company.html
Istithmar World PJSC acting Chief
Executive Officer Andy Watson said his company continues “to be
supportive of Loehmann’s.”  Istithmar is “actively working with management,
bondholders and other stakeholders to find a mutually agreeable
position to save the company,” Watson said, according to an e-
mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net  